The '''North American Nature Photography Association''' or '''NANPA''' is an organization dedicated to  of nature. It has several categories of membership, including discounts for students. It annually sponsors many events and conferences, such as NANPA Road Shows, in the United States. Its , initially established in 1997, awards scholarships, operates blinds for , and organizes funds in memory of deceased photographers and others. NANPA also markets books of interest to members, including those by members, through . 